        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\n3.3.9 is very old, as is 3.6. All the 3.X versions of Maven have security issues, but 4.x is still not production ready.\n\nUpgrading to 3.9.* would be best interim solution until 4.x is ready. That's work for Jessica and Andrew.",
